title: Paris Hilton Tease Eau De Parfum Spray by Paris Hilton, 1.7 Ounce
description: Introduced in the year 2010. Paris Hilton Tease Perfume by Paris Hilton, This floral chypre for women was created as an homage to marilyn monroe. It is sexy, yet innocent. It is a modern interpretation of glamorous 60s fragrances. Notes incorporate fuji apple, white peach, bergamot, white flowers, amber, blond wood and hot sand.
